Text: RE Im Leaving Enronof luck Mary you were a wonderful asset for PGE and Enron Original Message From mailto Sent None To KADDENCOM kaddencom WPPCorg Devon Kehoe TomO PAgov ernercom Subject Im Leaving Enron judy WPPORG MCIMAILCOM Date Fri Mar MessageID XMIMETrack Serialize by Router on ENEMTAEnronRelease December at PM MIMEVersion Contenttype textplain charsetusascii I am going to be the Senior Regulatory Counsel at ISO New England starting on April My last day in the Portland area will be March I enjoyed working with you and wish you the best of everything My new address will be Mary Hain Senior Regulatory Counsel ISO New England Inc One Sullivan Road Holyoke MA SONEcom
